casebody.data:
A. C. Israel Commodity Co., Inc. v. Jose E. Simao, Defendant. Banco Lisboa & Acores, Respondent.

Motion for stay dismissed as academic by virtue of the decisions of this court in Israel Commodity Co. v. Simao (9 A D 2d 676), and the stay contained in the order to show cause dated October 9, 1959 is vacated. Concur- — Breitel, J. P., M. M. Frank, Yalente, McNally and Stevens, JJ.
